<br>
In EQ your character information is saved very frequently. No matter how hard the crash when I come back I've never lost any items or time. It appears that DAoC does not save your character information as often as EQ does but then again I only lose time on the &quot;serious errors&quot; and not the ones that boot me to desktop. <br>
